      textEn: [
        "Therefore today\u2019s responsibility lies not with others but entirely with our youth. When the youth are wise, the nation is wise; when the youth are wealthy, the nation is wealthy; when the youth are strong, the nation is strong; when the youth are independent, the nation is independent; when the youth are free, the nation is free; when the youth progress, the nation progresses; when the youth surpass Europe, the nation surpasses Europe; when the youth dominate the globe, the nation dominates the globe.",
        "The red sun rises, its way shining bright. The river emerges from underground, rushing in a vast torrent. The hidden dragon leaps from the abyss, scales and claws flying. The young tiger roars in the valley, all beasts tremble. The falcon and hawk spread their wings, wind and dust are drawn in. Strange flowers first bud, resplendent and glorious. The great sword leaves the whetstone, its edge gleaming. Heaven is its canopy, earth its floor. Spanning a thousand ages in time, reaching the eight wildernesses in space. The future is like the sea; the days ahead are long.",
        "Beautiful indeed, our Young China, ageless as the heavens! Magnificent indeed, our Chinese youth, boundless as the nation!"
      ],
